[I] A lightweight full-featured web browser

[T] Opera is a full-featured Internet tool, most notably a fully standard
[T] conforming Web browser. Opera includes pop-up blocking, tabbed browsing,
[T] integrated searches, and advanced functions like a password manager,
[T] mouse gestures, native Scalable Vector Graphics (SVG) support, an email
[T] program, RSS newsfeeds, and IRC chat. It is designed to be fast and
[T] highly customizable.

